snippet: Andy Murray continued the defense of his title at Queen's Club on Friday, reaching the semifinals with a 6-4, 3-6, 6-1 victory against Kyle Edmund in an all-British match....
lead_paragraph: Andy Murray continued the defense of his title at Queen's Club on Friday, reaching the semifinals with a 6-4, 3-6, 6-1 victory against Kyle Edmund in an all-British match.
